            </h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">A visual exploration of the core capabilities driving customer security, product integrity, and compliance.</p>
        </header>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
